specification: Maruti Suzuki will give its best-selling model, the Alto 800 a mid-life makeover. Recent spyshots reveal the Alto 800's new face, that includes a redesigned headlamp cluster and a new bumper. The front bumper also has provisions for foglamps now, that was missing in the earlier iteration. The side and the rear profile remain unchanged.
name: Maruti 800

specification: The JCB 12v Drill Driver boasts 2 drill functions; drill and screwdriver with a 2 speed variable gearbox providing greater torque versatility for efficient drilling of various materials.  It has a maximum drilling capacity of 20mm in wood and 10mm in metal.  It comes with 2 x 1.3Ah Li-Ion battery packs and a 30 min quick charger. A LED light gives improved visibility and has a soft rubber overmould grip handle which provides comfort and a stable grip when working.
desc: JCB cordless 12v Li-Ion drill driver is best suited for drilling holes and driving screws into light and medium materials
name: DRILL DRIVER
